Nigerian entertainer, Denrele Edun, and award-winning singer, Yemi Alade, walked the runway at the first ever Africa Magic Viewers Choice Awards fashion show. The event, which marked day two of the eight-day event slated for this year’s AMVCA, was held on Sunday night at Victoria Island, Lagos. During the show, Yemi Alade and Denrele thrill the audience with their runway walk, amid cheers from the crowd. The video was shared on Africa Magic’s official Instagram page. Watch video below:  Copyright PUNCH. All rights reserved. This material, and other digital content on this website, may not be reproduced, published, broadcast, rewritten or redistributed in whole or in part without prior express written permission from PUNCH. Contact: theeditor@punchng.com